      "side": 1,
      "message": "I did it because manageExistingBot will be called thousands of times per minute, every minute. I don\u0027t want to run a transaction unless it\u0027s really necessary. vm was fetched prior to sending an RPC to Swarming. I fetch it again in case it\u0027s already had its Connected field set by some other task queue.\n\n1. Fetch model.VM\n2. Send RPC to Swarming\n3. Check vm.Connected (may be 1 sec out of date because fetch/check was separated by RPC)\n4. Re-fetch model.VM from dscache\n5. Check vm.Connected\n6. Run txn\n\nYou think it\u0027s overkill?",
